    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1916-05-25T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1916-05-25T00:00:00-05:00" n="859"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d859">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 341.622a/141</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Turkish Chargé</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_HAH1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hussein</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 4645/11</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-05-25">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 25, 1916</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: Referring to the note I had the honor to address
                    to the Department of State under yesterday’s date<note n="1" xml:id="d859fn1"
                        >Not printed.</note> in regard to the persons removed from the S. S. <hi
                        rend="italic">China</hi>, I beg leave to state that from advices received
                    through official German sources in Peking I was able to ascertain that the
                    Ottoman subjects among those removed are not supposed to be incorporated in the
                    armed forces of Turkey.</p>
                <p>Accept [etc.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_HAH1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">A. Hussein</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
